{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782210906797,"sessionID":"ses_10bf585e9fferjmNcR8To5cw5o","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_19ced3e92a124426a9cf4b79","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md","content":"---\ntitle: Deep Review Strategy\ndescription: Review strategy for 154-frontmatter-versioning spec folder\nsession_id: fanout-mimo-1782210787185-rpc3p9\n---\n\n# Deep Review Strategy\n\n## topic\nReview of Skill Frontmatter Versioning (154-frontmatter-versioning) — a phase-parent spec with 5 child phases that retroactively versions ~2,500 skill-doc frontmatter files and enforces a 4-part `version: X.Y.Z.W` standard.\n\n## review-dimensions\n- [ ] **D1 Correctness** — Logic errors, off-by-one, wrong return types, broken invariants\n- [ ] **D2 Security** — Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n- [ ] **D3 Traceability** — Spec/code alignment, checklist evidence, cross-reference integrity\n- [ ] **D4 Maintainability** — Patterns, clarity, documentation quality, ease of safe follow-on changes\n\n## completed-dimensions\n_(none yet)_\n\n## running-findings\n- **P0**: 0 (delta: 0)\n- **P1**: 0 (delta: 0)\n- **P2**: 0 (delta: 0)\n\n## what-worked\n_(populated during iterations)_\n\n## what-failed\n_(populated during iterations)_\n\n## exhausted-approaches\n_(populated during iterations)_\n\n## ruled-out-directions\n_(populated during iterations)_\n\n## next-focus\n**Dimension**: D1 Correctness\n**Files**: All 5 child phase spec.md files + parent spec.md\n**Rationale**: Correctness has highest blast radius — verify the spec logic, phase sequencing, handoff criteria, and requirement acceptance criteria are sound\n\n## known-context\n- Spec is Level 2 with 5 child phases, all marked \"Complete\"\n- Parent spec.md states all phases complete at 100%\n- The corpus is ~2,500 markdown files across `.opencode/skills/*/`\n- Version shape: 4-part `X.Y.Z.W` (skill-anchored, edit-count build segment)\n- Execution model: deterministic script + MiMo v2.5 Pro in-the-loop\n- `resource-map.md` not present. Skipping coverage gate.\n\n## cross-reference-status\n### Core (hard-gated)\n| Protocol | Status | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| spec_code | pending | Verify normative claims resolve to shipped behavior |\n| checklist_evidence | pending | No checklist.md found at parent level; check phase children |\n\n### Overlay (advisory)\n| Protocol | Status | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| feature_catalog_code | N/A | Not a skill target |\n| playbook_capability | N/A | Not a skill target |\n\n## files-under-review\n| File | Status | Notes |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| spec.md (parent) | pending | Phase parent spec |\n| 001-versioning-standard/spec.md | pending | Phase 1 — Versioning Standard |\n| 002-derivation-engine/spec.md | pending | Phase 2 — Derivation Engine |\n| 003-apply-core-skill-docs/spec.md | pending | Phase 3 — Apply Core Skill Docs |\n| 004-apply-catalogs-and-playbooks/spec.md | pending | Phase 4 — Apply Catalogs and Playbooks |\n| 005-verify-and-enforce/spec.md | pending | Phase 5 — Verify and Enforce |\n| graph-metadata.json | pending | Derived metadata |\n| description.json | pending | Memory description |\n\n## review-boundaries\n- **Max iterations**: 5\n- **Convergence threshold**: 0.10\n- **Stuck threshold**: 2\n- **Severity threshold**: P2\n- **Execution mode**: auto (fan-out lineage)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md","time":{"start":1782210906793,"end":1782210906796}},"id":"prt_ef40c4aa7001uxcjThFi6wq6jT","sessionID":"ses_10bf585e9fferjmNcR8To5cw5o","messageID":"msg_ef40c05d8001Y1pQG1nlWBJGsa"}}
