 tasks.md scaffold gap, graph-metadata status mismatch\n- **P2**: 3 (delta: +3) — missing checklist.md, file count inaccuracy, W-cap undocumented"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md\n@@ -10,19 +10,20 @@\n Review of Skill Frontmatter Versioning (154-frontmatter-versioning) — a phase-parent spec with 5 child phases that retroactively versions ~2,500 skill-doc frontmatter files and enforces a 4-part `version: X.Y.Z.W` standard.\n \n ## review-dimensions\n - [x] **D1 Correctness** — Logic errors, off-by-one, wrong return types, broken invariants\n-- [ ] **D2 Security** — Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n+- [x] **D2 Security** — Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n - [ ] **D3 Traceability** — Spec/code alignment, checklist evidence, cross-reference integrity\n - [ ] **D4 Maintainability** — Patterns, clarity, documentation quality, ease of safe follow-on changes\n \n ## completed-dimensions\n - **D1 Correctness** (Iteration 1): CONDITIONAL — 2 P1, 3 P2 findings. Tasks.md scaffolds stale; graph-metadata.json status mismatch.\n+- **D2 Security** (Iteration 2): PASS — 1 P2 advisory. Scripts use safe patterns (execFile with arrays, line-wise YAML parsing, no eval). Minor path boundary advisory.\n \n ## running-findings\n - **P0**: 0 (delta: 0)\n-- **P1**: 2 (delta: +2) — tasks.md scaffold gap, graph-metadata status mismatch\n-- **P2**: 3 (delta: +3) — missing checklist.md, file count inaccuracy, W-cap undocumented\n+- **P1**: 2 (delta: 0) — tasks.md scaffold gap, graph-metadata status mismatch\n+- **P2**: 4 (delta: +1) — missing checklist.md, file count inaccuracy, W-cap undocumented, path boundary advisory\n \n ## what-worked\n - Reading all implementation-summary.md files in parallel gave a complete cross-phase view of what was built and verified\n - Comparing spec.md metadata claims against graph-metadata.json and description.json revealed stale metadata\n","filediff":{"file":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md\n@@ -10,19 +10,20 @@\n Review of Skill Frontmatter Versioning (154-frontmatter-versioning) — a phase-parent spec with 5 child phases that retroactively versions ~2,500 skill-doc frontmatter files and enforces a 4-part `version: X.Y.Z.W` standard.\n \n ## review-dimensions\n - [x] **D1 Correctness** — Logic errors, off-by-one, wrong return types, broken invariants\n-- [ ] **D2 Security** — Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n+- [x] **D2 Security** — Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n - [ ] **D3 Traceability** — Spec/code alignment, checklist evidence, cross-reference integrity\n - [ ] **D4 Maintainability** — Patterns, clarity, documentation quality, ease of safe follow-on changes\n \n ## completed-dimensions\n - **D1 Correctness** (Iteration 1): CONDITIONAL — 2 P1, 3 P2 findings. Tasks.md scaffolds stale; graph-metadata.json status mismatch.\n+- **D2 Security** (Iteration 2): PASS — 1 P2 advisory. Scripts use safe patterns (execFile with arrays, line-wise YAML parsing, no eval). Minor path boundary advisory.\n \n ## running-findings\n - **P0**: 0 (delta: 0)\n-- **P1**: 2 (delta: +2) — tasks.md scaffold gap, graph-metadata status mismatch\n-- **P2**: 3 (delta: +3) — missing checklist.md, file count inaccuracy, W-cap undocumented\n+- **P1**: 2 (delta: 0) — tasks.md scaffold gap, graph-metadata status mismatch\n+- **P2**: 4 (delta: +1) — missing checklist.md, file count inaccuracy, W-cap undocumented, path boundary advisory\n \n ## what-worked\n - Reading all implementation-summary.md files in parallel gave a complete cross-phase view of what was built and verified\n - Comparing spec.md metadata claims against graph-metadata.json and description.json revealed stale metadata\n","additions":4,"deletions":3},"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-frontmatter-versioning/review/lineages/mimo/deep-review-strategy.md","time":{"start":1782211240754,"end":1782211240756}},"id":"prt_ef411632e001vuoLBfzxGiQb0p","sessionID":"ses_10bf585e9fferjmNcR8To5cw5o","messageID":"msg_ef41143fd001YGQ0cnNDs29b8R"}}
